quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,By the charging horses panting hard
  100,2,striking sparks from their flashing hooves
  100,3,raiding at full gallop in the early dawn
  100,4,leaving a trailing dust-cloud in their wake
  100,5,cleaving through the middle of the foe
  100,6,truly man is ungrateful to his Lord
  100,7,and indeed he bears witness to that
  100,8,Truly he is fierce in his love of wealth
  100,9,Does he not know that when the graves are emptied out
  100,10,and the heart´s contents are brought into the open
  100,11,that Day their Lord will certainly be aware of them